{"parse":{"title":"Next Education India Pvt. Ltd.","pageid":39395381,"revid":848952406,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"plainlinks metadata ambox ambox-content ambox-Advert\" role=\"presentation\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"mbox-image\"><div style=\"width:52px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Ambox_important.svg/40px-Ambox_important.svg.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Ambox_important.svg/60px-Ambox_important.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Ambox_important.svg/80px-Ambox_important.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"40\" data-file-height=\"40\" /></div></td><td class=\"mbox-text\"><div class=\"mbox-text-span\">This article <b>contains content that is written like <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:What_Wikipedia_is_not#Wikipedia_is_not_a_soapbox_or_means_of_promotion\" title=\"Wikipedia:What Wikipedia is not\">an advertisement</a></b>.<span class=\"hide-when-compact\"> Please help <a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Next_Education_India_Pvt._Ltd.&amp;action=edit\">improve it</a> by removing <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Spam\" title=\"Wikipedia:Spam\">promotional content</a> and inappropriate <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:External_links\" title=\"Wikipedia:External links\">external links</a>, and by adding encyclopedic content written from a <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Neutral_point_of_view\" title=\"Wikipedia:Neutral point of view\">neutral point of view</a>.</span>  <small><i>(February 2014)</i></small><small class=\"hide-when-compact\"><i> (<a href=\"/wiki/Help:Maintenance_template_removal\" title=\"Help:Maintenance template removal\">Learn how and when to remove this template message</a>)</i></small></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Next Education India Pvt Ltd, head-quartered in <a href=\"/wiki/Hyderabad\" title=\"Hyderabad\">Hyderabad, India</a>, is a firm that offers learning solutions for students across <a href=\"/wiki/K%E2%80%9312_(education)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"K\u201312 (education)\">K\u201312</a>.\n</p><p>The company staffs are 1200 people who design teaching aids for classrooms as well as self-learning packages. Currently, there are 10,000 learning modules across several subjects taught at school-level. Currently, there is an investment of Rs. 2500 <a href=\"/wiki/Crore\" title=\"Crore\">crores</a> by the firm for its research and development activities. It reaped a revenue of over 100 crores in 2012.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Products_And_Services\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Products And Services</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Awards\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Awards</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Products_And_Services\">Products And Services</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Next_Education_India_Pvt._Ltd.&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Products And Services\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>TeachNext is a digital classroom solution which makes the end-to-end process of teaching and learning easy and more engaging. .<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>LearnNext is a computer based interactive, independent and intelligent learning solution for students of classes 6 to 12. Maths, Science, Social Science and English lessons of CBSE, ICSE and all other State Boards of India have been covered in an interesting animated format.<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>NextLab is an experiential learning approach enabling students to use hands-on activities to better understand English Maths, Science and Robotics.<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>NextERP/NLP is a school management software for smooth running of school administration.<sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>NextBooks, an integrated curriculum solution, is a series of textbooks for the pre-primary and primary school years.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Awards\">Awards</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Next_Education_India_Pvt._Ltd.&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Awards\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Next Education is a recipient of the following awards:\n</p>\n<ul><li>eIndia K-12 Public Choice Award 2012 (Category: Interactive Solution Provider) <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>eIndia K-12 Public Choice Award at e-India Awards Gujarat \u2013 2011 (Category: Best Assessment Tool provider)<sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Best Multimedia Content for K-12 Education, World Education Summit 2012<sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Best Digital Multimedia Content \u2013 K12 segment at Wisitex India Shiksha Ratna E-Learning Summit 2011<sup id=\"cite_ref-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Corporate-Innovation in Teaching Pedagogy Award, World Education Summit April- 2013<sup id=\"cite_ref-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Excellent Human Resource Management in Education Industry, By National HRD Network, Patna Chapter in 2012</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Next_Education_India_Pvt._Ltd.&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">StudyGuideIndia.Com. (2013, January 1). StudyGuideIndia.Com. Retrieved from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.studyguideindia.com/News/Education/News-details.asp?NID=14646&amp;NY=2013\">http://www.studyguideindia.com/News/Education/News-details.asp?NID=14646&amp;NY=2013</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">TeachNext, Multimedia Learning Software for CBSE Schools and Students. (n.d.). Retrieved from InfoPiper.Com&#160;: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://infopiper.com/teach-next-multimedia-learning-software-for-cbse-syllabus-schools-and-students/\">http://infopiper.com/teach-next-multimedia-learning-software-for-cbse-syllabus-schools-and-students/</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">(n.d.). Retrieved from EducationWorld.In: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.educationworld.in/product/ict/digital-classroom-solutions/teach-next.html\">http://www.educationworld.in/product/ict/digital-classroom-solutions/teach-next.html</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">(2012, September 1). Retrieved from IndiaMart.Com: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://news.indiamart.com/story/next-educations-learnnext-provide-kerala-boards-content-166998.html\">http://news.indiamart.com/story/next-educations-learnnext-provide-kerala-boards-content-166998.html</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Maths to easier at MathsLab. (2013, April 12). Hans India. Retrieved from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.thehansindia.com/2013/04/12/maths-to-get-easier-at-mathslab/\">http://www.thehansindia.com/2013/04/12/maths-to-get-easier-at-mathslab/</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Indran, N. (December 5, 2012). Retrieved from ApnNews.Com: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.apnnews.com/2012/12/05/next-education-organizes-an-e-learning-seminar-for-principals-in-the-city/\">http://www.apnnews.com/2012/12/05/next-education-organizes-an-e-learning-seminar-for-principals-in-the-city/</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a h